duplicate: <p>
There's a typo in your <code>add_cap()</code> example: <code>edit_ranking_strings</code> should be <code>edit_ranking_settings</code>.
</p>
<p>
You should also add this in order to be able to save the settings:
</p>
<pre class="wiki">function ranking_option_page_capability( $capability ) {
	return 'edit_ranking_settings';
}
add_filter( 'option_page_capability_ranking_options_group', 'ranking_option_page_capability' );
</pre><p>
See <a class="closed ticket" href="http://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/14365" title="#14365: enhancement: Admin custom option screen not saved unless user manage_options capability (closed: fixed)">#14365</a>.
</p>
